<h1>Thief Caravans Game</h1>
<p>Can you find and steal from the caravans? Click the button to search for a caravan!</p>

<button id="searchButton">Search for a Caravan</button>
<button id="bribeButton">Make a Bribe</button>

<div id="result"></div>
<div id="beansCount">Beans Grabbed: 0</div>
<div id="lastBribe">Last Bribe Amount: 0</div>

<script>
    const searchButton = document.getElementById('searchButton');
    const bribeButton = document.getElementById('bribeButton');
    const resultDiv = document.getElementById('result');
    const beansCountDiv = document.getElementById('beansCount');
    const lastBribeDiv = document.getElementById('lastBribe');

    let totalBeans = Math.floor(Math.random() * 500) + 50; // Random starting amount between 50 and 549
    let beansGrabbed = 0;

    const caravans = [
        { loot: 100, caught: false },
        { loot: 50, caught: false },
        { loot: 200, caught: false },
        { loot: 30, caught: false },
        { loot: 0, caught: true }, // Represents a caravan where the player got caught
    ];

    searchButton.addEventListener('click', function() {
        // Randomly choose a caravan
        const caravan = caravans[Math.floor(Math.random() * caravans.length)];

        // Determine the result
        if (caravan.caught) {
            resultDiv.innerHTML = "Oh no! You got caught while trying to steal!";
            searchButton.disabled = true; // Disable the search button
        } else {
            beansGrabbed += caravan.loot;
            totalBeans -= caravan.loot;
            resultDiv.innerHTML = "Success! You stole " + caravan.loot + " beans!";
            beansCountDiv.innerHTML = "Beans Grabbed: " + beansGrabbed;
        }
    });

    bribeButton.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const bribeAmount = Math.floor(Math.random() * 50) + 10; // Random bribe between 10 and 59
        totalBeans += bribeAmount;
        lastBribeDiv.innerHTML = "Last Bribe Amount: " + bribeAmount + " beans";
        resultDiv.innerHTML = "You made a bribe and received " + bribeAmount + " beans! You are now free to continue stealing.";

        // Enable the search button again to allow further attempts at stealing
        searchButton.disabled = false;
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>
```

### Key Updates:
1. **Bribe After Being Caught**: After getting caught, players can make a bribe, which allows them to be free again and continue searching for caravans.
2. **Last Bribe Amount Display**: The amount of the last successful bribe is displayed, so players can keep track of how much they have bribed.

This format provides more strategic options for players and enhances overall gameplay!

